---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <Hero
    heading="About NeuroImpact Therapeutics"
    subHeading="Breakthrough Science for a Better Tomorrow."
  />
  <section>
    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Transforming Lives Through Targeted Therapeutics</h2>
      <p>
        At NeuroImpact Therapeutics, we are dedicated to transforming the lives
        of patients suffering from neurological disorders by pioneering the
        development of targeted, precision-driven therapeutics.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Advancing Ion Channels Research</h2>
      <p>
        By leveraging cutting-edge structural biology and a deep understanding
        of ion channels and disease-associated proteins, we aim to unlock novel
        pathways for treating debilitating conditions such as Alzheimerâ€™s and
        epilepsy.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Our Vision for Neurological Disorder Treatment</h2>
      <p>
        Our vision is to revolutionize the treatment of neurological disorders,
        enabling a future where effective therapeutics improve lives worldwide.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our mission is to bridge innovation and impact, delivering
        groundbreaking solutions that address unmet medical needs and restore
        hope to patients and their families.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Core Values</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Innovation:</strong> Driving breakthroughs in science and medicine.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Collaboration:</strong> Partnering with researchers and institutions
          to accelerate progress.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Patient-Centric Approach:</strong> Focusing on improving lives
          and addressing unmet medical needs.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Scientific Excellence:</strong> Leveraging cutting-edge research
          and expertise.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Call for Partnership</h2>
      <p>
        We welcome collaborations with academic institutions, industry leaders,
        and investors who share our passion for advancing neurological health.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>
        At NeuroImpact Therapeutics, we are committed to making a meaningful
        impact on the lives of patients, families, and the broader medical
        community. Together, we can change the future of neurological care.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    h2 {
      margin-block-end: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-gradient-start);
      width: fit-content;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
    }
    ul li {
      margin-block-end: 10px;
    }
    ul li strong {
      color: var(--clr-gradient-end);
    }

    .content-section {
      margin-block-end: 56px;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
